_sText:
This is a small floating aim map, both spawns are protected by a small shelter, wheres a roof ontop where you can climb.
In middle theres a bridge where you can go to the other side, and if you fall, you die.
Weapons avaible are ak47 and m4a1.

..This map was rushed, so it could have been better..

EDIT: I added walls and changed the skybox to militia_hdr, looks more friendly now though its a bit darker than before.
